% Find the largest number among three numbers
Start
Declare variables a,b and c.
Read variables a,b and c.
If a>b
   If a>c
      Display a is the largest number.
   Else
      Display c is the largest number.
   Else
   If b > c
      Display b is the largest number.
    Else 
      Display c is the largest number.
 Stop.
 
